Bicaranya cuma mutar-mutar,

00:15:45.949 --> 00:15:47.325
bilangnya "gangguan radio',"

00:15:47.408 --> 00:15:48.826
"kebetulan," tapi aku...

00:15:48.910 --> 00:15:50.870
Aku tahu cara pikirmu kreatif.

00:15:50.954 --> 00:15:53.206
Entah harus minta tolong ke siapa lagi.

00:15:53.289 --> 00:15:54.707
Mereka menyuruhmu kesini karena...?

