Aku datang ke sini atas...

00:15:56.000 --> 00:15:57.126
Itulah ironisnya.

00:15:57.210 --> 00:15:58.711
Monarch tak mau akui...

00:15:58.795 --> 00:16:00.880
aku membantu mengalahkan Mechagodzilla,

00:16:00.964 --> 00:16:02.924
