Aku lebih pantas dari setengah
pekerja di sana.

00:16:20.692 --> 00:16:23.740
Aku sudah tahu rencana Godzilla
sebelum orang Monarch bilang...

00:16:23.820 --> 00:16:26.447
Makanya aku kemari, Bernie.

00:16:26.531 --> 00:16:28.449
Aku kesini. Oke?

00:16:31.160 --> 00:16:32.787
Bisa bantu, tidak?

00:16:33.496 --> 00:16:34.789
Tergantung.

00:16:34.872 --> 00:16:36.833
Kau bos barunya di Mess?

00:16:36.916 --> 00:16:38.167
Apaan itu?

00:16:38.251 --> 00:16:39.544
Monarch Hollow Earth Station.

00:16:39.627 --> 00:16:41.421
MHES, si Mess.

