00:17:12.493 --> 00:17:14.454
Maaf, suntingan akhir?
Tidak.

00:17:13.676 --> 00:17:15.676 line:20%
<c.colora2ff00><b>Peringatan Titan!
Kondisi Godzilla Meningkat Drastis!
Mohon Petunjuk!</b></c>

